# NAME: Rithmic
# AUTHOR: Kevin (kevshen13)
# REPO: https://github.com/kevshen13/surge-rules
# DESCRIPTION: Rithmic rule list for Surge
# UPDATED: 2026-04-22
# MAINTENANCE: Maintain this list by traffic purpose and route behavior.
# RULE: Include Rithmic platform processes, official domains, gateway hosts, and stable IP ranges used by Rithmic feeds and execution.
# RULE: Keep vendor-specific IP ranges here when they are already validated in the live config.
# SOURCE: Rithmic firewall advisory lists official R | Trade Execution Platform IP ranges and required ports.

PROCESS-NAME,R Trader
PROCESS-NAME,R Trader Pro
PROCESS-NAME,R | Trader Pro
PROCESS-NAME,RTraderPro
PROCESS-NAME,Rithmic Trader
PROCESS-NAME,Rithmic Trader Pro
